# LonaNote Android BottomSheetModal mitigation notes:
# - This patch keeps the minimal BottomSheetBody opacity guard, the Backdrop floor guard,
#   and the #2690 containerHeight sync attempt for historical mitigation.
# - Real-device testing still reproduces invisible content / backdrop-only states under
#   heavy Android sheet open-close cycles.
# - Do not treat this patch as a reliable fix; migrate heavyweight Android sheet hosts
#   away from @gorhom/bottom-sheet instead of expanding this patch further.
